@ModelImportedVariable(name="currentTotalPowerProduced",type=java.lang.Double.class) @ModelImportedVariable(name="currentTotalPowerConsumed",type=java.lang.Double.class) @ModelExportedVariable(name="totalPowerStored", type=java.lang.Double.class) public class BatteryElectricityModel extends fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.AtomicHIOA
The class BatteryElectricityModel defines a simulation model for the electricity production/consumption of the Battery.

Description

The electric power production (in Wats) depends upon the production components (SolarPanel and PetrolGenerator). The consumption depends upon the others components such as CookingPlate, Lamp, AirConditioniong and Fridge. .

Initially, the electric power stored is at 0.0 Wh.

  • Imported events: none
  • Exported events: none
  • Imported variables: none
  • Exported variables: name = totalPowerStored, type = Double
